{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🔧 SDK vs 非 SDK 两种 Debug 方式\n",
    "\n",
    "> 非 SDK 是"直接开车"；SDK + API 是"通过远程控制系统开车"。\n",
    "> 车本身可以是同一辆，但驾驶方式不同。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 📋 两种运行方式概览\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "非 SDK 版本：\n",
    "ipynb 里直接创建 graph\n",
    "↓\n",
    "graph.invoke / graph.stream\n",
    "↓\n",
    "结果直接在 notebook 里显示\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "SDK 版本：\n",
    "terminal 先 langgraph dev\n",
    "↓\n",
    "启动 LangGraph API server: localhost:2024\n",
    "↓\n",
    "ipynb 用 langgraph_sdk client 连接它\n",
    "↓\n",
    "client.runs.stream(...)\n",
    "↓\n",
    "结果在 notebook 里显示\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "它们的 **graph 逻辑本质一样**，区别是运行方式不同。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📊 核心区别对比表\n",
    "\n",
    "| 对比 | 非 SDK / notebook 本地运行 | SDK + LangGraph API |\n",
    "|------|------|------|\n",
    "| 调用方式 | `graph.stream(...)` | `client.runs.stream(...)` |\n",
    "| graph 在哪里 | 当前 notebook 内存里 | `langgraph dev` server 里 |\n",
    "| 配置来源 | notebook 代码 | `langgraph.json` |\n",
    "| 更像什么 | 单机调试 | production 调试 |\n",
    "| thread / run 管理 | 你手动传 config | API 帮你管理 |\n",
    "| 多用户/多任务 | 不适合 | 更接近真实场景 |\n",
    "| Studio 支持 | 弱 | 强 |\n",
    "| 适合阶段 | 学概念、快速实验 | 学部署、API、SDK、真实调用链 |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🖥️ 非 SDK 版本适合什么？\n",
    "\n",
    "适合学习核心概念："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 非 SDK 版本 - 直接调用 graph object\n",
    "# graph.stream(...)\n",
    "# graph.get_state(...)\n",
    "# graph.update_state(...)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "好处：\n",
    "- 简单、直接、容易看清 graph 本身怎么运行\n",
    "\n",
    "缺点：\n",
    "- 不太像真实线上 agent 系统"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🌐 SDK 版本适合什么？\n",
    "\n",
    "SDK 版本更接近 production："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# SDK 版本 - 通过 client 调用远程 API\n",
    "# client.threads.create()\n",
    "# client.runs.stream(...)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "它让你学习：\n",
    "- assistant\n",
    "- thread\n",
    "- run\n",
    "- hosted graph\n",
    "- API server\n",
    "- remote execution\n",
    "- Studio 调试方式\n",
    "\n",
    "也就是：graph 被部署/托管以后，外部程序怎么调用它。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🎯 学习顺序建议\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "先用非 SDK 版本理解 graph / state / checkpoint / interrupt\n",
    "↓\n",
    "再用 SDK 版本理解 API / thread / run / assistant / deployment\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "> **最重要的一句话：**\n",
    "> 非 SDK 是"直接开车"；SDK + API 是"通过远程控制系统开车"。\n",
    "> 车本身可以是同一辆，但驾驶方式不同。🚗"
   ]
  }
 ],
